{"ts": "2026-06-05T20:39:00.000Z", "event": "report", "msg": "L2 report assembly", "agent": "report-l2", "tokens_in": 1556, "tokens_out": 709, "elapsed_ms": 19586, "model": "qwen/qwen3-235b-a22b-2507", "prompt": "You are the Level 2 Report agent. Merge all worker results into a clean Markdown report.\n\n## Worker Results\n### ux\nAll files are in place. Here's a complete summary of what was created:\n\n---\n\n## ✅ Complete Build Summary\n\n### 📁 Files Created\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `content_brief.json` | Full design system spec + page content (copy, image prompts, layout structure) |\n| `index.html` | Semantic, accessible HTML page with all 6 sections |\n| `styles/main.css` | Full design token system + responsive layout + a11y-ready styles |\n| `images/hero-banner.jpg` | Generated hero image |\n| `images/product-mug.jpg` | Product image — Stoneware Mug |\n| `images/product-throw.jpg` | Product image — Linen Throw |\n| `images/product-bowls.jpg` | Product image — Bowl Set |\n| `images/product-board.jpg` | Product image — Serving Board |\n\n---\n\n### 🧩 Content Brief (`content_brief.json`) Details\n\n**Design System:**\n- **Colors**: Warm earth tones — `#8B6F47` primary, `#C76B4D` terracotta accent, `#D4A853` gold highlight\n- **Typography**: Playfair Display (headings) + Inter (body) with fluid `clamp()` scale\n- **Spacing**: Fluid responsive spacing throughout\n- **Shadows**: Warm-toned `rgba(58, 46, 36, ...)` shadows for depth\n\n**6 Sections with Real Copy:**\n1. **Hero** — \"Sustainably Crafted for Life's Quiet Moments\" with dual CTA buttons\n2. **Benefits** — 3-column: Sustainably Sourced, Handcrafted with Care, Timeless Design\n3. **Subscription** — 3 tiers ($28/quarter, $48/month featured, $120/month) with feature lists\n4. **Reviews** — 5-star testimonials from Elena V., Marcus T., Priya K.\n5. **Shop** — 4 products: Mug ($34), Throw ($89), Bowls ($72), Board ($56)\n6. **Footer** — Brand, 3 link columns, newsletter signup, social links\n\n---\n\n### ♿ Accessibility Features\n\n- **Semantic HTML**: `<nav>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, `<footer>`, `<header>` throughout\n- **Logical heading hierarchy**: `h1` → `h2` → `h3` — no skips\n- **ARIA**: `aria-label`, `aria-labelledby`, `aria-expanded`, `aria-hidden`, `aria-controls`, `aria-current`\n- **Skip link**: First focusable element on page\n- **Focus styles**: 3px `:focus-visible` outline with offset on all interactive elements\n- **Keyboard nav**: Tab-order, Escape closes mobile nav, focus management\n- **Color contrast**: Text meets 4.5:1 minimum against backgrounds\n- **`prefers-reduced-motion`**: Disables all animations for motion-sensitive users\n- **Form labels**: Proper `<label>` with `htmlFor` on newsletter input\n- **Role attributes**: `role=\"list\"`, `role=\"listitem\"`, `role=\"banner\"`, `role=\"navigation\"`, etc.\n\n---\n\n### 🎨 CSS Highlights\n\n- **Custom Properties**: Complete design tokens on `:root` — colors, fonts, spacing, shadows, radii\n- **Fluid Typography**: `clamp()` for all heading sizes — no breakpoints needed\n- **Responsive Grid**: CSS Grid with auto-adjusting columns (4→3→2→1)\n- **Content Visibility**: `content-visibility: auto` for below-fold performance\n- **GPU Animations**: `transform` + `opacity` only; `will-change` used sparingly\n- **No `!important`**: Clean specificity throughout\n- **Hover states**: Cards lift with `translateY(-6px)` + shadow transitions\n\n---\n\n### 🖼️ Generated Images\n\nAll 5 images were generated via Gemini — the hero banner, 4 product shots — and saved to `images/`.\n\n### html\n[frontend-html-30624c4a-d727-4b51-8b4f-4119b5d90dcf] Exceeded max tool iterations (12)\n\n### css\nBoth files are written successfully. Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## ✅ Product Benefits & Subscription Sections — Complete\n\n### `index.html` — Updated (683 lines)\n- **Benefits Section** (`#benefits`): 3-column grid with SVG icons (leaf, shield, compass) in circular wrappers, headings, and descriptive text\n- **Subscription Section** (`#subscription`): 3-tier pricing cards with:\n  - **Billing Toggle**: Accessible `role=\"radio\"` toggle between Monthly/Annual pricing with smooth knob animation and \"Save up to 20%\" badge\n  - **The Seasonal** ($28/mo → $25/ann): 4 features, tertiary CTA\n  - **The Monthly** ($48/mo → $40/ann, **Featured**): \"Most Popular\" badge, 5 features, primary CTA, elevated card style\n  - **The Collector** ($120/mo → $100/ann): 6 features, tertiary CTA\n  - Each card has SVG icons, checkmark feature lists with inline SVGs, and full-width CTAs\n- **Toggle Script**: JavaScript handles `aria-checked` state, updates prices/periods from `data-*` attributes, supports keyboard (Enter/Space)\n\n### `styles/main.css` — Updated (1220 lines)\n- **Benefits enhancements**: SVG icon wrappers with hover scale/background transitions\n- **Billing toggle**: Custom toggle switch with `aria-checked` styling, smooth knob animation (`cubic-bezier` spring), active label highlighting\n- **Subscription cards**: Flexbox column layout with `flex-grow: 1` on feature lists, featured card scaling, responsive breakpoints\n- **Responsive**: Mobile (single column, centered), Tablet (2-col with featured full-width), Desktop (3-col)\n- **Accessibility**: `prefers-reduced-motion` disables all transforms/transitions, `:focus-visible` outlines, semantic `role` attributes\n- **Performance**: `content-visibility: auto` on all sections\n\n## Files Created\n- content_brief.json: {\n- images/hero-banner.jpg: JPEG image\n- images/product-board.jpg: JPEG image\n- images/product-bowls.jpg: JPEG image\n- images/product-mug.jpg: JPEG image\n- images/product-throw.jpg: JPEG image\n- index.html: <!DOCTYPE html>\n- styles/main.css: /* ===================================================\n- run.log: {\"ts\": \"2026-06-05T20:25:58.000Z\", \"event\": \"workspace_created\", \"msg\": \"Workspace: /home/aymen/Desk\n\n## Guidelines\n- Group results by worker\n- Include summary table with